name: water-blocks
description: <!-- const findMaxWalls = (index, walls) => {   let maxLeft = 0;   let maxRight = 0;     for (let i = index - 1; i >= 0; i--){       if (walls[i] > maxLeft) {         maxLeft = walls[i];       }     }     for (let i = index + 1; i < walls.length; i++){       if (walls[i] > maxRight) {         maxRight = walls[i];       }     }   return [maxLeft, maxRight]; }
